flowchart TD
    K[Kernel] --> S[Service Supervisor]
    S --> UI[UI Shell]
    S --> NET[Network Service]
    S --> FS[Storage Service]
    S --> GPU[Graphics Driver Service]
    S --> AI[AI Model Service]
    UI -->|crash| S
    NET -->|crash| S
    FS -->|fault| R[Rollback/Repair]
    GPU -->|hang| G[Reset/Fallback]
    AI -->|runaway| Q[Quota/Revoke Caps]
